summary: This document is an email correspondence between Jeanne Brennan and Amanda Kirby regarding the confirmation of an incoming wire transfer from JPMorgan to Southern Financial. The email confirms the receipt of the wire and includes a note about the confidentiality of the communication.

persons.name: Jeanne Brennan
persons.context: Jeanne Brennan is the sender of the email confirming the receipt of an incoming wire transfer.

persons.name: Amanda Kirby
persons.context: Amanda Kirby is the recipient of the email and is confirming the details of the incoming wire transfer.

keyFacts: The email confirms the receipt of an incoming wire transfer from JPMorgan to Southern Financial.
The correspondence is marked as confidential.
The communication includes a note about the prohibition of unauthorized copying or distribution.
